          <h3>Output: Logits → Token</h3>
          <p>The final hidden state feeds into an <strong>unembedding matrix</strong> producing logits over the vocabulary. Softmax converts to probabilities. <strong>Temperature</strong> controls randomness. Then one token is sampled.</p>
          <div style="margin-top:12px;display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
