          <div class="arch-block" style="--bc:var(--cyan);">Clean Image</div>
        </div>
        <p class="arch-desc">State-of-the-art image generation. Classifier-free guidance enables text conditioning. DDIM/LCM reduce steps dramatically.</p>
        <div class="arch-uses">Stable Diffusion, DALL·E 3, Midjourney, FLUX</div>
